Output visuals/out/spinner.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 18
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 24

Hide
Type "cd /app/projects/glyph/repo"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Type "go run -tags glyph_story ./components/spinner/story/"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
